structure.unit: OFFENSES AGAINST THE STATE AND PUBLIC JUSTICE

law.history: Repealed 1962 Ky. Acts ch. 234, sec. 61. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 1372.
